window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><i>How to Encourage Yourself Through Any Problem With Biblical Truths: A Guide to Understanding Faith-Filled Words</i> is a fast listen, but it packs quite a punch and can literally change your life. Negative self starts in the heart, is conceived in the mind and destroys lives - but it doesn't have to. </p> <p>This book offers a guide to stopping negative self-talk by replacing thoughts of doubt with inspiration and positive, faith-filled words. </p> <p>A very inspiring book that motivates, strengthens, enlightens and encourages us to believe that when we have faith that God is for us, nothing can be against us.</p>"; 
